---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Ed Barlow — Ed Barlow">
  <section class="home-intro">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h1 class="home-name">Ed Barlow</h1>
      <div class="home-body">
<p><strong>AI Enabled Career Principal Engineer</strong> Looking For <strong>Consulting</strong> or <strong>Senior Platform/Data Roles</strong> <br></p>
<p>I reworked my <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Process-Based-Database-Administration-Management-ebook/dp/B073RRQBZC">Process Based Methedology</a> 
using my scale-proven <a href="https://webcloudstudio.github.io/webcloudstudio/project-docs/Specifications/Features.html">Technology Rules Engine</a>
using a Full <a href="https://webcloudstudio.github.io/webcloudstudio/project-docs/Specifications/white-paper.html">Specification Driven Design Process</a> </p>
<ul>
    <li>Endpoint Exposure - Service Catalog, Django/Rest Unified Proxy</li>
    <li>Workflow And /specification Based Design by PROCESS</li>
    <li>Bug Fix Workflow via Agent Transation Log feed to /specifications</li>
    <li>Scaled Automation, Logging, Operations, and Monitoring for all your projects</li>
    <li>Consistent Documentation, Scheduling, and Build Pipelines</li>
    <li>Agent Enforced Seamless Standard Conformity</li>
    <li><b>SELF ITERATION WORKFLOW</b>: find missing features->rank->define->implement one->review</li>
    <li>Metrics</li>
</ul>

<p>Previously: <strong>Principal Engineer/Director</strong> at major hedge funds, investment banks, insurance companies, and startups </p>
<p><strong>Author</strong>, <strong>Speaker</strong>, <strong>Free Software Developer</strong></p>
<p>Expert at all aspects of data processing, data <strong>E</strong></p>
<h2>Feature Workflow</h2>
<p><img src="/webcloudstudio/diagrams/v3-feature-workflow.png"> </p>
<h2>Project Definition</h2>
<p><img src="/webcloudstudio/diagrams/v3-project-definition.png" ></p>
<h2>AI Workflow</h2>
<p><img src="/webcloudstudio/diagrams/v3-ai-workflow.png" ></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .home-intro { padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }

    .home-name {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin: 0 0 2rem;
    }

    .home-body { max-width: 860px; }

    .home-body p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .home-body h2 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .home-body ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .home-body li {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .home-body li::before {
      content: '—';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .home-body strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

    .home-body em {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
